	 1. What is Local class?
	 * class inside one block is called local class.
	 * aa classes ki manam access modifer ga abstract and final e rendea use chestamu.
	 * manam e local classes constructor block lo kuda petukoachu.
	 * manam e local classes non-static block lo kuda petukoachu.
	 * manam e local classes static block lo kuda petukoachu.
	 * local classes lopala vaka non-static method create chaiyavachu, static method create chestea error
	   vastadi.
	 * e local classes ni class ki bayata access chaiyaleamu.
	 * name or peru leani dani anonymous antamu.
	 */

